*.jfr
*.jsonl

# Raw per-cell benchmark data (JFR recordings + latency logs, ~153GB total,
# individual files up to 4.7GB) is far too large for git -- it's hosted on
# Zenodo instead. Only the small aggregated summary that backs every table
# and figure in the report is versioned here.
data/*
!data/results/
data/results/*
!data/results/aggregate.csv
